snippet.title: Jett Rider: Official Animated Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Enjoy the animated launch trailer for Jett Rider, an arcade shooter packed with action, exploration, RPG elements, tons of humor and awesome bosses. Explore, fight, gain experience, purchase weapons in this exciting adventure. Jett Rider launches on PC, Nintendo Switch, Xbox, and PlayStation on January 25.

#IGN #Gaming #JettRider #Animated
